### Phase 2: Role Constants — Code Update

#### [MODIFY] [roles.ts](file:///d:/suzuky/apps/portal/src/lib/auth/roles.ts)

**Changes:**
- Update `ROLE_LEVELS` to match new DB hierarchy
- Update `ROLE_GROUPS`: add `DEALER_INTERNAL` group for all dealer-scoped staff
- Update helper functions: [isAnyAdmin()](file:///d:/suzuky/apps/portal/src/lib/auth/roles.ts#140-143) → platform admins only (level ≤ 6), add `isDealerAdmin()` for dealer-scoped admins
- Add new helper: `requiresDealerId(role)` — returns true if the user MUST have a dealer_id

