### Phase 4: Auth System Updates

#### [MODIFY] [get-user.ts](file:///d:/suzuky/apps/portal/src/lib/auth/get-user.ts)

Add validation: If the user's role is a dealer-scoped role but they have no `dealer_id`, block access.

```typescript
export async function getCurrentUser() {
    // ... existing code ...
    
    const dealerId = profile?.dealer_id || payload.dealerId || null;
    
    // Enforce dealer_id for dealer-scoped roles
    if (requiresDealerId(payload.role) && !dealerId) {
        console.error(`[AUTH] User ${payload.userId} has role ${payload.role} but no dealer_id`);
        return null; // Block access
    }
    
    return {
        ...payload,
        dealerId,
        fullName: profile?.full_name || null,
        isDealerScoped: requiresDealerId(payload.role),
    };
}
```

#### [MODIFY] [middleware.ts](file:///d:/suzuky/apps/portal/src/middleware.ts)

Update route guards to prevent dealer-scoped roles from accessing super-admin routes.

#### [MODIFY] [permissions.ts](file:///d:/suzuky/apps/portal/src/lib/auth/permissions.ts)

Add dealer_id scoping to permission checks.

