### Phase 5: API Route Audit

Every API route under `/api/v1/` must:
1. Call [getCurrentUser()](file:///d:/suzuky/apps/portal/src/lib/auth/get-user.ts#5-30) to get the authenticated user
2. Check `user.role` for authorization
3. Scope ALL Prisma queries with `where: { dealer_id: user.dealerId }`

#### Key routes to update:

| Route | File | Status |
|-------|------|--------|
| `/api/v1/workshop/*` | `src/app/api/v1/workshop/` | Likely already scoped ✅ |
| `/api/v1/technician/*` | `src/app/api/v1/technician/` | Needs audit |
| `/api/v1/dealer/*` | `src/app/api/v1/dealer/` | Needs audit |
| `/api/v1/dashboard/*` | `src/app/api/v1/dashboard/` | Needs audit |
| `/api/super-admin/*` | `src/app/api/super-admin/` | Should show ALL dealers |

