### Phase 6: Frontend Isolation (Future)

- **Per-dealer dashboard**: Each dealer sees only their own stats
- **Super admin dashboard**: See all dealers, switch between them
- **Sidebar navigation**: Role-based menu items
- **Dealer selector**: Super admin can switch dealer context

